{"tid":1565953,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"細思極恐—港鐵有計劃逼害本地粵語人口","createTime":"2019-09-13T10:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T02:03:32.000Z","uid":276716,"like":146,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"d80d0c9831bff4077a48006c1a39b1910a5a49c6","tid":1565953,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TTzVxtZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTTzVxtZ.jpg&h=706b6bf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個掛住笑popo熱綫被封，你地唔記得呢單駭人聽聞嘅新聞，就係港鐵公然宣布喺招聘時會排斥本地粵語族群。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190913/mobile/bkn-20190913000136206-0913_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190913%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190913000136206-0913_00822_001.html&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=623b06d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190913/mobile/bkn-20190913000136206-0913_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n港鐵理由係避免乘客講粗口會刺激到職員，所以會選用唔識粵語嘅尼泊爾人。呢個明顯係不成理由，因為乘客若果有心挑釁，講句英文粗口有何難。<br />\n<br />\n我估計，港鐵真正目的係想名正言順咁逼害本地粵語族群，達致兩個效果。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1.只聘請非粵語族群擔任執法者</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 所有粵語人士都係潛在暴徒，要接受非粵語人士的監管及執法</span><br />\n<br />\n如果計劃成功，呢個做法可以擴大到所有公職人員，例如警察、救護、海關、入境處等，都可以用同一個理由去排斥粵語族群。<br />\n<br />\n留意尼泊爾人嘅人數唔多，冇可能請到咁多尼仔做執法角色。咁邊個地方嘅人係唔識粵語，又可以大量供應去擔任公職呢？相信計劃最終目的都呼之欲出。"},{"pid":"6ac0aa02bd03a28e650550ac3523a8e96987227f","tid":1565953,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:55:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=2fc97b49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區集合地點!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n油麻地、佐敦、尖沙咀: 梳士巴利公園(太空館附近)<br />\n荃灣、大窩口、青衣: 荃灣公園(海濱長廊)、青衣海濱長廊<br />\n葵興、葵芳、荔景: 林士德遊樂場、葵涌運動場<br />\n美孚: 嶺南之風<br />\n太子、旺角: 花墟公園<br />\n荔枝角、長沙灣: 長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗: 通州街公園<br />\n油塘、藍田: 油塘道遊樂場<br />\n將軍澳、寶琳、坑口、康城<br />\n中西區（西區、中環、金鐘、半山、山頂）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"9dd04488d4e1102ae862502d135430c008a93e76","tid":1565953,"uid":265192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:56:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">G20團隊呈獻 ：<br />\n連登眾籌熱烈祝賀中国70大壽！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/g20celebratemotherbirthday/?fbclid=IwAR2beWbo6b5DN0Z78c8hOOnD6gjlUGwmfDGrGbnvaN2lrt61PxH2AYZHVEo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fg20celebratemotherbirthday%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2beWbo6b5DN0Z78c8hOOnD6gjlUGwmfDGrGbnvaN2lrt61PxH2AYZHVEo&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=56a46920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/g20celebratemotherbirthday/?fbclid=IwAR2beWbo6b5DN0Z78c8hOOnD6gjlUGwmfDGrGbnvaN2lrt61PxH2AYZHVEo</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qEfYvkN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqEfYvkN.jpg&h=5f96d463&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa6ae1b6c5b2af29ba38bf4cf2b1a4b7b06bc6ef","tid":1565953,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:01:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠